---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About AI Creator Stack — Independent AI Tool Reviews"
  description="AI Creator Stack publishes independent, hands-on reviews of AI tools for content creators. Learn how we test, rate and choose the tools we recommend."
  canonicalPath="/about"
>
  <div class="container prose">
    <h1>About AI Creator Stack</h1>
    <p>
      AI Creator Stack is an independent review site for the AI tools that content creators
      actually use — the ones that help YouTubers, TikTokers, bloggers and podcasters go from
      a blank page to a published piece of content faster.
    </p>

    <h2>Why we exist</h2>
    <p>
      New AI tools launch every week, each promising to save you hours. Most creators don't have
      the time to trial ten different apps before committing. We do that work for you: we group tools
      by where they fit in the creator workflow — writing, video, voice, design and SEO — and give you
      an honest read on what each one is genuinely good at, what it costs, and who it's for.
    </p>

    <h2>How we test</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>We cross-check every factual claim — pricing, features, platform support — against at least two sources, including each tool's official website.</li>
      <li>We write every review from scratch. We never copy specs or paragraphs from other review sites.</li>
      <li>We date-stamp each review so you know when its pricing and features were last verified. SaaS pricing changes often, so we always link you back to the official site to confirm the latest.</li>
      <li>Our "best for" verdicts reflect the type of creator each tool suits — not who pays us the most.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How we make money</h2>
    <p>
      AI Creator Stack is reader-supported. Some of the links on our site are affiliate links, which
      means we may earn a commission if you subscribe to a tool through them — at no extra cost to you.
      Affiliate relationships never determine our rankings or ratings. Read our full
      <a href="/affiliate-disclosure">affiliate disclosure</a> for details.
    </p>

    <h2>Get in touch</h2>
    <p>
      Spotted an out-of-date price, or want us to review a tool? <a href="/contact">Contact us</a> —
      we read every message.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
